<!-- 1.1.14 -->
<div class="toload example">
<p><span class="envidentifier">Example 1.1.14</span>
A preorder $R$ on a set $X$, regarded as a category as in Example <span class="ref" data-tag='examplepreordersarecategories'></span>, is a groupoid if and only if $R$ is an equivalence relation. (See <span class='ref' data-tag='definitionprincipalgroupoid'></span> below.)
</p>
</div>